<tr class="bg1"><td>&nbsp;</td><td><a  href='http://dbtropes.org/resource/Film/Gladiator/int_1281a637'>Film: Gladiator / int_1281a637</a></td>
<td><div title='http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment'>comment</div></td>
<td><i>Alone With Prisoner Ploy: When Lucilla arrives at Maximus' cell, she tells him &quot;rich matrons pay well to be pleasured by the bravest champions&quot;. He has been chained up in preparation for her visit. In fact she's there to tell him there is a growing conspiracy against Commodus, and to ask him to meet a politician who's involved.</i></td>
</tr>


